These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, metal, d&b, classical
1. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of classical##1
2. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | metal | reggae | classical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, goldfish, horse, lizard
1. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the snake##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Pet   | snake | horse | goldfish | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, hiking, writing, reading
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | writing | video-games | hiking | reading |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, boat, car, taxi
1. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Transport   | car | scooter | boat | taxi |

 #################################

 
